Class ConstantVelocityModelSlamCalibrator

java.lang.Object
com.irurueta.ar.slam.BaseSlamCalibrator<ConstantVelocityModelSlamCalibrationData>
com.irurueta.ar.slam.ConstantVelocityModelSlamCalibrator
public class ConstantVelocityModelSlamCalibrator extends BaseSlamCalibrator<ConstantVelocityModelSlamCalibrationData>
Processes data to estimate calibration for constant velocity model SLAM estimator. This class must be used while gathering data for a system being kept constant (no motion).
